f s > best_strength:\n            best_strength = s\n            best_idx = i\n\n    return f\"{entity_label}.{augmentations[best_idx]}\"\n\nUsage example (based on your examples):\n- Strongest_Extension(\"Slices\", [\"SErviNGSliCes\", \"Cheese\", \"StuFfed\"]) -> \"Slices.SErviNGSliCes\"\n- Strongest_Extension(\"my_entity\", [\"AA\", \"Be\", \"CC\"]) -> \"my_entity.AA\"\n\nIf you’d like, I can also provide a tiny test harness you can run locally.","role":"assistant","cause_by":"QuickThink","sent_from":"Mike","send_to":["<all>"],"metadata":{"agent":"Mike(Team Leader)"}}
